Usage: create_module_model [-help] [-allow_port_mismatch] [-cell <string>]
                           [-phys_hier] [-tag <string>] [-type <string>]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-allow_port_mismatch        # (bool, optional)
-cell <string>              # <Specifies cell name to save. By default, current
                            # top cell will be saved. This option should only
                            # be used for 3DIC design and child partitions.>
                            # (string, optional)
-phys_hier                  # create whole hdb (bool, optional)
-tag <string>               # <flow tag> (string, optional)
-type <string>              # <type of module model> lef flexIlm ilm pnr etm
                            # 1801 spef mmmc boundary_model pnr_shell scan_info
                            # latency timing_context extraction_context
                            # pin_assign gds (string, optional)